-02T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"唔知點解今次係咁吹風一定要維園出發。明明呢支歌仔無唱好耐。"},{"pid":"f6fc74407f1cd4cc6091b4f4f533de4e4b5340cb","tid":1807503,"uid":271593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"一點幾去到維多利亞公園<br />\n入到去已經係企喺個台附近 但係都要三點幾先離開到維園<br />\n差唔多6點到中環"},{"pid":"d5b4280c6ae3d48e0c472522ea17a084a4f41e22","tid":1807503,"uid":46033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"行到SOGO 就收左皮啦, 排隊入維園都排左2個幾鐘"},{"pid":"ac6a7a0fbf3c647477b59baeea31c5e930f7d382","tid":1807503,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cabfd2c5feca2dd633dc73fd13a2d39b9978aec","tid":1807503,"uid":51612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"唔知點解今次係咁吹風一定要維園出發。明明呢支歌仔無唱好耐。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"去到天后, 係咁有人叫要入維園, 之後有人話民陣有人講狗總都有數人頭, 咁咪唔入直行啦, 去到皇仁, 又有人叫一定要入維園, 玩撚謝"},{"pid":"bcd1f095fe5eac5ed584e23bf62e82644eaa0f2a","tid":1807503,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:29:38.000Z","msg":"點解係起步點<br />\n唔係終點 點"},{"pid":"11a853c8cddff207182297a2a75e01e3bc020163","tid":1807503,"uid":320251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"4點30到維園"},{"pid":"444db97d018798e2b674cc9e9cd10e1c001e3e5f","tid":1807503,"uid":166900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:31:18.000Z","msg":"入維圜排左四個小時，去到sogo 就被取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吊高佢仲要30mins  緊急疏散"},{"pid":"0d4e124b06fd9c62f43a02bea64e0f81a5d585b4","tid":1807503,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d7e4c7462ba7b8dc6673d5a6329f7f8e7dc1445","tid":1807503,"uid":61099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"有冇成功出到閘既巴打分享下尋日咩情況 後排又係咩環境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:31:25.000Z","msg":"嗰陣好早到 差唔多1300就到咗維園<br />\n企喺工會旗後面<br />\n其實嗰陣只係個出口好細 要跨過個健身器材嗰個位<br />\n一出到中央圖書館就好多位 企喺度跳舞都得<br />\n跟住連啲平時塞位<br />\neg. 八爪魚橋+Sogo都唔係好塞<br />\ncut不反嗰段時間<br />\n咁啱喺修頓位<br />\n最後行到1830順利到遮打道"},{"pid":"aa924847c9425840d798e590feee41c603b9c51f","tid":1807503,"uid":84172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 <br />\n2:00入維園 到佢開咪宣布腰斬都仲排緊隊岀返去<br />\n完全上唔到網唔知岀面咩事 淨係靠隔離啲人口耳相傳話灣仔打緊<br />\n有frd 遲過我到天后，但係一早行左岀去行緊。我就仲塞左係入面"},{"pid":"cfefee5d7bc6477c8e437ef363571710b9f5980d","tid":1807503,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f303af24689eed9e1938de9f2d9ac1bd4564156","tid":1807503,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a47a3cefc2ca68eca02901f251f33f8addf4bb","tid":1807503,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T04:55:36.000Z","msg":"其實我想知前面係咪真係行緊<br />\n<br />\n2:30已經喺維園去到6點都仲係維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾十萬人塞咗喺嗰度幾個鐘完全唔知前面發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"約4點45係灣仔hsbc見住D綠曱甴衝入黎<br />\n5點兜路行番遊行路線<br />\n5點07放tg，已經斷左條隊<br />\n我5點20分行到終點，應該係最後一批可以行晒全程"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:35:51.000Z","msg":"最後一批應該係1830到遮打嗰班<br />\n嗰陣我地好多人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">聽到好多廣東話唔正嘅伯伯婆婆嗌香港人向前行！ 行埋落去！多人就唔驚！</span><br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae366cf88a9734335ff40f5273a94623430185c","tid":1807503,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"同樓主情況一樣<br />\n最慘係上唔到網 咩消息都唔知<br />\n到左5點幾話中止開始散<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9d933931b9b36c50542f7ddf923b8be2e6f015","tid":1807503,"uid":143976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"2點到維園, 5點15分到出到圖書館, 差唔多到sogo被腰斬<br />\nbtw用smartone都有一半時間上到網"},{"pid":"d14b88a9cbbfe818a27c5ca5cb4cd495dcec8d4f","tid":1807503,"uid":326665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:40:08.000Z","msg":"其實大家又想要人數靚，又想舒服根本無可能。<br />\n你插隊，民陣報細數又屌人，唔插隊，又屌民陣安排差。又想民陣計埋插隊人數係好難㗎，咁多人。<br />\n<br />\n樂觀睇，昨日個數字咁靚我覺得係維園出發係值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4ccd487767277c0417ae979eea2e1196f7b415","tid":1807503,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"三點去到 經小食亭行緩步徑<br />\n行行下出到去網球場嗰邊<br />\n行行下出埋去圖書館對出<br />\n行到銅鑼灣就話唔撚準遊行<br />\n過程兩個幾三個鐘<br />\n<br />\n網球場企定定三個黑警好招搖<br />\n（非捉鬼 但真係個個行過都話狗有樣睇）"}]}